<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
    <script defer src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>सम्पर्क सूत्र - UPITI Employees Association</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 font-sans flex flex-col min-h-screen">

    <header class="bg-white shadow-md border-b-4 border-blue-700">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center md:justify-between">
             <div class="flex items-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
                <img src="/logo.png" alt="UPITI Logo" class="h-32 w-auto object-contain">
            </div>
            <div class="text-center flex-1 px-4">
                <h1 class="text-5xl text-red-600 font-bold mb-2">उत्तर प्रदेश औद्योगिक प्रशिक्षण संस्थान कर्मचारी संघ</h1>
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-400 mb-1">UTTAR Pradesh Industrial Training Institute Employees Association.</h2>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">(उ0 प्र0 शासन, श्रम अनुभाग-6, संख्या 482/36-6-207/71 लखनऊ दिनांक 1 मार्च, 1974 द्वारा मान्यता प्राप्त)</p>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">सम्बद्ध: राज्य कर्मचारी संयुक्त परिषद, उत्तर प्रदेश</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="bg-blue-800 text-white shadow-lg sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center md:justify-start space-x-1 md:space-x-6 py-3 text-sm md:text-base font-medium">
                <li><a href="/index" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">मुख्य पृष्ठ</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">हमारे बारे में</a><li>
                <li><a href="/organization" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">संगठन संरचना</a></li>
                <li><a href="/events" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">घटनाक्रम</a></li>
                <li><a href="/gallery" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">गैलरी</a></li>
                <li><a href="/orders" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">शासनादेश / आदेश</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:bg-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded transition">सम्पर्क सूत्र</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 flex-grow">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-800 border-b-4 border-red-500 inline-block pb-2">सम्पर्क सूत्र (Contact Us)</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">अपने सुझाव, समस्याएं या विचार हमारे साथ साझा करें। हम आपकी आवाज़ को सशक्त बनाने के लिए यहाँ हैं।</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
            
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-t-4 border-blue-700">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">कार्यालय का पता</h3>
                    
                    <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
                        <div class="bg-blue-100 p-3 rounded-full mr-4 text-blue-700">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800">प्रांतीय मुख्यालय</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1 leading-relaxed">
                                उत्तर प्रदेश औद्योगिक प्रशिक्षण संस्थान कर्मचारी संघ<br>
                                (राजकीय ITI परिसर)<br>
                                लखनऊ, उत्तर प्रदेश
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
                        <div class="bg-red-100 p-3 rounded-full mr-4 text-red-600">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800">ईमेल आईडी</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">
                                <a href="mailto:upitien@gmail.com" class="hover:text-blue-700 transition">upitien@gmail.com</a>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div class="bg-green-100 p-3 rounded-full mr-4 text-green-600">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-phone text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800">हेल्पलाइन नंबर</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">+91 XXXXX XXXXX (कार्यालय समय)</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-200 w-full h-64 rounded-xl shadow-inner border border-gray-300 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-gray-500">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot text-5xl mb-2"></i>
                    <p class="font-medium">यहाँ Google Map एम्बेड किया जा सकता है</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 border-l-4 border-red-600 pl-3">हमें संदेश भेजें</h3>
                
                <form action="#" method="POST" class="space-y-5">
                    <div>
                        <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">पूरा नाम (Full Name) *</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition">
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="branch" class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">संस्थान / शाखा का नाम (ITI Name) *</label>
                        <input type="text" id="branch" name="branch" required class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition" placeholder="उदा: GITI अलीगंज, लखनऊ">
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
                        <div>
                            <label for="mobile" class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">मोबाइल नंबर *</label>
                            <input type="tel" id="mobile" name="mobile" required class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">ईमेल आईडी</label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="subject" class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">विषय (Subject) *</label>
                        <select id="subject" name="subject" required class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition bg-white">
                            <option value="">-- विषय चुनें --</option>
                            <option value="grievance">समस्या / शिकायत (Grievance)</option>
                            <option value="suggestion">सुझाव (Suggestion)</option>
                            <option value="membership">सदस्यता संबंधी (Membership)</option>
                            <option value="other">अन्य (Other)</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">आपका संदेश (Message) *</label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition"></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-red-600 transition duration-300 shadow-md flex justify-center items-center">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane mr-2"></i> संदेश भेजें
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300 py-8 border-t-4 border-blue-700 mt-auto">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-4">UPITI Employees Association</h4>
                <p class="text-sm">राज्य कर्मचारी संयुक्त परिषद, उत्तर प्रदेश से संबद्ध एक प्रमुख कर्मचारी संगठन।</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
                <h4 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-4">Connect With Us</h4>
                <div class="flex space-x-4">
                    <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-blue-500 transition shadow">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-sky-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-sky-400 transition shadow">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-red-500 transition shadow">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-right">
                <h4 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-4">Visitor Statistics</h4>
                <div class="inline-block bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 px-4 py-2 rounded text-xl font-mono text-green-400 tracking-widest shadow-inner mb-2">
                    211131
                </div>
                <br>
                <div class="inline-block bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 px-4 py-2 rounded text-xl font-mono text-green-400 tracking-widest shadow-inner">
                    0000000
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-gray-800 text-center text-xs text-gray-500">
            &copy; 2026 UTTAR Pradesh Industrial Training Institute Employees Association. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
